name: [LIST-OF] As a user, I should add default column in dashboard params
fullName: JIT-Dashboard-002a-LISTOF-default-column.[LIST-OF] As a user, I should add default column in dashboard params

steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitdash002" and Comment "Testing"
When I navigate to menu "Dashboard app" without submenu
Then I should see Dashboard screen display
Then I should see table Name "jitdash002" displayed in dashboard list
When I select table Name "jitdash002" in dashboard table list
When I toggle on switcher of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002"
Then I should see option value "jitdash002s.updated_at,jitdash002s.created_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to display" index "1" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002"
Then I should see option value "jitdash002s.updated_at,jitdash002s.created_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to Search" index "1" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002"
Then I should see option value "jitdash002s.updated_at,jitdash002s.created_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Order by" index "1" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002"
Then I should see option value "Asc,Desc" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Order by" index "2" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002"
When I select multi dropdown label "Params to display" index "1" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002" by value "jitdash002s.created_at"
Then I should see option value "jitdash002s.updated_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to display" index "1" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002"
Then I should NOT see option value "jitdash002s.created_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to display" index "1" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002"
When I clear selected option value "jitdash002s.created_at" with index "1"
Then I should NOT see option value "jitdash002s.created_at" with index "1" displayed
Then I should see option value "jitdash002s.updated_at,jitdash002s.created_at" displayed in multi dropdown menu label "Params to display" index "1" of item "List of" with table Name "jitdash002"
When I click general any span text button label "Select Table Columns" with index "1"
Then I should see option value "jitdash002s.created_at,jitdash002s.updated_at" with index "1" displayed
When I clear selected option value "jitdash002s.created_at,jitdash002s.updated_at" with index "1"
Then I should NOT see option value "jitdash002s.created_at,jitdash002s.updated_at" with index "1" displayed
When I click general any span text button label "Select Associated Columns" with index "1"
Then I should see option value "jitdash002s.created_at,jitdash002s.updated_at" with index "1" displayed
